# 📱 3. iOS & Android Support

Mobile devices are essential for MFA, email, and Teams.

### **Common Tasks**
- MFA setup  
- Email profile configuration  
- Company Portal / Intune enrolment  
- App permissions  
- VPN mobile profiles  

### **iOS Troubleshooting**
- Reset network settings  
- Offload/reinstall apps  
- Check Screen Time restrictions  
- Check iCloud Keychain conflicts  

### **Android Troubleshooting**
- Clear app cache  
- Reset Google Play Services  
- Check battery optimisation (can block notifications)  
- Re‑register device in Company Portal  

